PrecisAppointment of Garth Dawley, of Winnipeg, Manitoba, as a full-time member of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years; designation of the said Garth Dawley for the Manitoba/Saskatchewan region, as established under subsection 10(1.1) of that Act; and determine that he shall reside within 100 kilometres of the Manitoba/Saskatchewan regional office, effective April 13, 1993.
